snippet: A government ban on foreign investors has scuttled Australia’s biggest land sale, an official said on Friday.
abstract: Officials say Australian ban on foreign investors has disqualified sale of S Kidman & Company, which would have been largest land sale in nation's history.
lead_paragraph: A government ban on foreign investors has scuttled Australia’s biggest land sale, an official said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Foreign Ownership Ban Prevents Australia Land Sale
headline.main: Foreign Ownership Ban Prevents Australia Land Sale
